# Memory

Long-term notes the agent has gathered about the user, ongoing work, and
context that should persist across conversations.

The agent will append to this file over time as it learns. It's also fine to
seed it manually with facts you want the agent to remember from day one.

## Examples of what belongs here

- Recurring projects or interests
- Decisions you've already made (so the agent doesn't re-ask)
- People, places, tools you reference often
- Preferences the agent should respect
